title: OctopuoS Genesis Supply = 888
body:
Change the supply to be broken up into 2 generations. First 888 will be Genesis. The remainder will be part of a second generation release at a future point. 

Max supply of contract will remain at 8,888. Sale will be paused once we reach the 888 minted mark (website will reflect 888 on counter). 

All first 888 genesis tokens will get the "Origin: Genesis" attribute to distinguish them from future editions on the same contract. 

This is similar to Kongz, Kaiju's etc. where 2 generations are kept on the 1 smart contract.
author: 0xd7B233b03e6A3e4be7D989387E5144495B9a7E64
